Police said the man is at this stage only considered a person of interest in the case.

No details have been released about the child's cause of death. However, Rainwater said they do consider the death 'suspicious.'

The neighborhood was in shock after the child's death, which came days after another local toddler was killed.

'It is very shocking,' Empress Ming told the Journal Constitution. 'I can't believe it.'

